  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TNT20">
<l>tērāḷum vāḷarakkaṉ celvam māḷat</l>
<l>teṉṉilaṅkai muṉmalaṅkac centī yolki</l>
<l>pōrāḷa ṉāyirantōḷ vāṇaṉ māḷap</l>
<l>porukaṭalai yaraṇkaṭantu pukku mikka</l>
<l>pārāḷaṉ pāriṭantu pārai yuṇṭu</l>
<l>pārumiḻntu pāraḷantu pārai yāṇṭa</l>
<l>pērāḷaṉ pērōtum peṇṇai maṇmēl</l>
<l>peruntavatta ḷeṉṟallāl pēca lāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[This] girl who chants the names of the renowned one</l>
<l rend="indent">who rules the world, having dug up [that] world, eaten the world,</l>
<l>Spit out the world [again and] measured the world,</l>
<l rend="indent">[of] the man of war who, having kindled a hot blaze so that Lanka to the south</l>
<l>Once trembled to end the wealth of the sword[-bearing] demon who mastered the chariot,</l>
<l rend="indent">as the ruler of the world flourished having traversed the defenses</l>
<l>Of the crashing seas [and] entered [Śoṇitapura] to end [the life of] thousand-armed Bāṇa,</l>
<l rend="indent">besides calling [her] the great[est] ascetic on earth, can one speak [at all]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
